plot: The comical misadventures of a family that owns a bar: the downright stupid and uneducated Miro Pereira, his sensible wife Balbina and Balbina's brother Antón, who's always inventing the most absurd plans to make easy money, always involving his brother-in-law Miro, who invariably blows them.   Written by  Karahde Khan
